    <p>{`After being declared, validation libraries can be used in a validation profile document using the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`uses`}</inlineCode>{` RAML property and providing an alias for the library
Notice that a name for the data shape or function constraint connected to the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`validations`}</inlineCode>{` property  will still be required to be able to use the data shape.`}</p>
